text:
if you're looking for an upscale denny's, look no further. if you're looking for denny's, it's actually not that far from the grand lux. the short walk should not deter you! (right outside between venetian's and harrah's or HURRAH'S as some would say.)

this place is great for group dining since there's hella seating available. average is about the best way i can describe the food though.

it sure is convenient though at 2am when you'd rather not have little cards slapped at you or solicitation heading back to your room. ah vegas baby.
